title: No. 8 Alabama survives scare from Tennessee, 19-14 (Yahoo Sports)
text: Posts: 54,510 No. 8 Alabama survives scare from Tennessee, 19-14 (Yahoo Sports) Derrick Henry and Alabama only dominated the last few minutes, when their national championship hopes were hanging by a thread. Henry scored on a 14-yard run with 2:24 left and the eighth-ranked Crimson Tide held on for a 19-14 victory over Tennessee on Saturday with an overpowering finish in a game that was surprisingly close most of the way. It sets up a showdown with No. 5 LSU in two weeks at Bryant-Denny Stadium, where Alabama (7-1, 4-1 Southeastern Conference) has been at its most vulnerable.
